{"about_the_game":"San de Ville, a village haunted by a recent increase in shatanist activity, hosts a chilli-eating contest. Quella, a little-known streamer, decides to document the event and meets the competition's front-runner: Father Orlok.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675670/extras/paski_ORLOK__1_.png?t=1724958493\" /><br><br>Heavy Duty is written in the form of a mockumentary that will make you shiver with cringe. There is talking to the camera, there is a village drama, there are TV strips like in BBC. It's hard to believe this really happened.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675670/extras/paski_QUELLA.png?t=1724958493\" /><br><br>You play as Father Orlok, sharing a slice of your life. Let me put it this way, it's not one of the most exciting jobs in the world, but at least it pays well. Especially since everyone is afraid of you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675670/extras/paski_DOGFERATU.png?t=1724958493\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Beat shatanists.<br></li><li>Fight the boss.<br></li><li>Test your weird weapons.<br></li><li>Destroy everything (well, almost).<br></li><li>Wash off shatanic graffiti.<br></li><li>Collect money from the faithful.<br></li><li>Drive a strange car.<br></li><li>Perform an exorcism.<br></li><li>Consume alcohol.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675670/extras/paski_SHATANIST.png?t=1724958493\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":" I Wanna Rock","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1675670/ebe5be1c8b9d6297438cd6adddf7181a76f4bba7.jpg"},{"name":"Blessed are the sick","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1675670/65e8582574c6bc6a25f44b200644e6389182fa05.jpg"